<p>must have fired over a hundred shells. They were spitting all round him first a flash &amp; then a cloud of smoke but he sailed away seemingly unscathed. It was a beautiful night although a little cloudy. We went for a spin through the crops outside the village it was great.</p>
<p>2/7/16.<br/>Took the bikes out for exercise last night &amp; thoroughly enjoyed the ride along the country roads through the beautiful crops. Soon after we arrived back a heavy bombardment commenced not far from here. It shook the windows &amp; doors &amp; kept going until about 4 o'c this morning. It was believed to be in the vicinity of La Bassee. An occasional flash could be seen from the back door.</p>
